snippet: A Pennsylvania coroner made the ruling in the death of the student, Chun Deng, who officials say sustained a brain injury in December during a fraternity ritual in the Pocono Mountains.
abstract: Death of Baruch College freshman Chun Deng in Psi Delta Psi fraternity ritual in Pennsylvania is ruled homicide.
lead_paragraph: A Pennsylvania coroner made the ruling in the death of the student, Chun Deng, who officials say sustained a brain injury in December during a fraternity ritual in the Pocono Mountains.

headline.main: Baruch College Student’s Death Is Ruled a Homicide
headline.print_headline: Student’s Death Is Ruled a Homicide
